1
00:00:10,960 --> 00:00:13,420
♪The maple mark on your skin♪

2
00:00:14,230 --> 00:00:17,040
♪The only proof we exist♪

3
00:00:18,210 --> 00:00:21,450
♪I stole you back from destiny♪

4
00:00:21,560 --> 00:00:24,430
♪But can I redeem myself♪

5
00:00:24,430 --> 00:00:26,540
♪I don't care what fate foretells♪

6
00:00:26,750 --> 00:00:30,330
♪Or how rough the road may be♪

7
00:00:30,340 --> 00:00:33,280
♪Stay, I'll fight for you♪

8
00:00:33,610 --> 00:00:37,660
♪That's all I'll ever do♪

9
00:00:37,760 --> 00:00:39,890
♪If life is just a show♪

10
00:00:39,890 --> 00:00:42,650
♪I'll stay with you till the end♪

11
00:00:42,650 --> 00:00:44,980
♪I'm scared we'll wake up alone♪

12
00:00:44,980 --> 00:00:47,960
♪So don't let this dream end♪

13
00:00:47,960 --> 00:00:52,420
♪In my bones, in my heart♪

14
00:00:52,420 --> 00:00:54,100
♪I know I'll have to leave♪

15
00:00:54,100 --> 00:00:55,670
♪You must not leave my side♪

16
00:00:55,670 --> 00:00:57,260
♪No place can hold us in♪

17
00:00:57,260 --> 00:01:01,910
♪Not when it's you and me♪

18
00:01:06,890 --> 00:01:10,400
♪Forever♪

19
00:01:11,490 --> 00:01:15,250
♪In my soul♪

20
00:01:17,260 --> 00:01:23,300
=This Palace Maid Isn't Very Calm=
=Episode 4=

21
00:01:27,310 --> 00:01:28,150
Mother.

22
00:01:34,920 --> 00:01:37,200
You look pale today.

23
00:01:37,870 --> 00:01:39,310
Feeling unwell?

24
00:01:39,400 --> 00:01:40,680
Shall I call the physician

25
00:01:41,150 --> 00:01:42,120
for you?

26
00:01:42,680 --> 00:01:43,680
Mother.

27
00:01:44,120 --> 00:01:44,960
No need.

28
00:01:45,000 --> 00:01:46,790
I just didn't sleep well.

29
00:01:50,680 --> 00:01:52,070
Greetings, Your Highness.

30
00:01:52,230 --> 00:01:53,200
Greetings, Prince.

31
00:01:53,950 --> 00:01:56,590
Your Highness, breakfast is ready.

32
00:01:57,000 --> 00:01:58,280
And this Calming Tea

33
00:01:58,280 --> 00:02:01,120
is specifically for the Prince.

34
00:02:03,480 --> 00:02:04,320
Your Highness.

35
00:02:04,510 --> 00:02:05,710
It has

36
00:02:05,710 --> 00:02:07,560
lily, jujube, and sour jujube seed

37
00:02:07,790 --> 00:02:09,400
to relieve anxiety.

38
00:02:09,520 --> 00:02:11,310
It's perfect for poor sleepers.

39
00:02:11,470 --> 00:02:12,310
Anxiety?

40
00:02:13,560 --> 00:02:15,470
How do you know I sleep poorly?

41
00:02:15,750 --> 00:02:16,590
Remember?

42
00:02:16,870 --> 00:02:18,360
I took your pulse.

43
00:02:20,280 --> 00:02:21,120
Your Highness.

44
00:02:21,310 --> 00:02:22,560
He's suffering

45
00:02:22,560 --> 00:02:23,910
from anxiety.

46
00:02:24,310 --> 00:02:25,280
Overthinking

47
00:02:25,280 --> 00:02:26,360
and a restless mind.

48
00:02:26,360 --> 00:02:27,710
Trouble falling asleep,

49
00:02:27,710 --> 00:02:29,150
and nightmares.

50
00:02:29,430 --> 00:02:30,360
It will only

51
00:02:30,360 --> 00:02:32,800
lead to frequent headaches.

52
00:02:32,800 --> 00:02:33,910
Is that true?

53
00:02:34,560 --> 00:02:35,400
Son.

54
00:02:35,710 --> 00:02:37,870
Why didn't you tell me?

55
00:02:38,000 --> 00:02:38,840
Mother.

56
00:02:39,360 --> 00:02:40,200
I didn't

57
00:02:40,870 --> 00:02:42,030
want you to worry.

58
00:02:43,360 --> 00:02:44,200
Ruizhu.

59
00:02:44,630 --> 00:02:46,240
Call the physician.

60
00:02:48,280 --> 00:02:49,120
No need

61
00:02:49,750 --> 00:02:51,190
to look elsewhere.

62
00:02:51,590 --> 00:02:53,470
Ye Jin says she can cure it,

63
00:02:53,960 --> 00:02:55,910
so let her try.

64
00:02:56,910 --> 00:02:58,910
Can you really?

65
00:02:59,750 --> 00:03:01,280
Worth a try.

66
00:03:01,560 --> 00:03:02,750
But…

67
00:03:03,240 --> 00:03:04,630
I have one condition.

68
00:03:05,120 --> 00:03:06,470
I'm not bargaining.

69
00:03:06,710 --> 00:03:07,590
It's just

70
00:03:07,590 --> 00:03:09,870
a rule I have.

71
00:03:09,870 --> 00:03:12,120
The patient must cooperate.

72
00:03:12,590 --> 00:03:13,590
If I'm constantly

73
00:03:13,590 --> 00:03:15,360
doubted or interrupted,

74
00:03:15,360 --> 00:03:16,310
then,

75
00:03:16,310 --> 00:03:17,710
I can't treat you.

76
00:03:17,710 --> 00:03:18,550
How dare you?

77
00:03:20,310 --> 00:03:21,960
Setting rules for your master?

78
00:03:22,840 --> 00:03:24,190
That's a first.

79
00:03:28,520 --> 00:03:29,870
You have nerve

80
00:03:29,870 --> 00:03:31,190
and quite the mouth.

81
00:03:31,590 --> 00:03:33,190
But I value talent.

82
00:03:33,400 --> 00:03:34,400
Today,

83
00:03:34,630 --> 00:03:36,400
show us how much

84
00:03:36,800 --> 00:03:38,400
real skill lies

85
00:03:38,680 --> 00:03:40,400
behind the rule of yours.

86
00:03:40,750 --> 00:03:41,590
Yes.

87
00:03:47,930 --> 00:03:48,800
Your Highness.

88
00:03:48,800 --> 00:03:49,640
Prince.

89
00:03:49,800 --> 00:03:52,190
This is a sachet I made.

90
00:03:52,190 --> 00:03:53,470
Lavender calms,

91
00:03:53,470 --> 00:03:55,800
citrus peel regulates qi,
and polygala clears the mind.

92
00:03:56,080 --> 00:03:58,400
I've tested the ratio myself.

93
00:03:58,590 --> 00:04:00,800
Very effective for insomnia.

94
00:04:03,280 --> 00:04:04,360
This bamboo stick is modeled

95
00:04:04,360 --> 00:04:07,800
(Fictional. Do not imitate.)
after an auricular acupoint stimulator.

96
00:04:07,800 --> 00:04:09,680
With ear acupressure,

97
00:04:09,680 --> 00:04:11,590
it stimulates nerves to treat insomnia.

98
00:04:11,590 --> 00:04:12,800
Simple,

99
00:04:12,870 --> 00:04:14,000
but effective.

100
00:04:14,520 --> 00:04:15,430
This thing

101
00:04:15,680 --> 00:04:17,040
seems flimsy.

102
00:04:17,560 --> 00:04:18,800
Can it cure me?

103
00:04:18,800 --> 00:04:20,600
Try it and see.

104
00:04:23,950 --> 00:04:25,750
I'm starting.

105
00:04:29,920 --> 00:04:30,760
Your Highness.

106
00:04:30,950 --> 00:04:32,160
I have insomnia.

107
00:04:33,240 --> 00:04:34,600
Not an ear problem.

108
00:04:37,490 --> 00:04:38,340
Your Highness.

109
00:04:38,360 --> 00:04:39,870
You promised to cooperate.

110
00:04:39,870 --> 00:04:40,720
Are you going back

111
00:04:40,720 --> 00:04:41,560
on your word already?

112
00:04:41,920 --> 00:04:42,870
I am not.

113
00:04:45,040 --> 00:04:46,270
Then let's begin.

114
00:04:50,430 --> 00:04:52,160
(He's shy.)

115
00:04:52,160 --> 00:04:53,270
(So innocent.)

116
00:04:55,160 --> 00:04:56,000
Your Highness.

117
00:04:56,160 --> 00:04:58,680
I'm pressing the Shenmen point now.

118
00:04:58,720 --> 00:05:00,040
This might sting a bit.

119
00:05:00,480 --> 00:05:01,320
Stay with me

120
00:05:01,630 --> 00:05:02,950
and breathe.

121
00:05:03,310 --> 00:05:04,920
Inhale.

122
00:05:06,480 --> 00:05:08,390
Exhale.

123
00:05:09,950 --> 00:05:12,000
Inhale.

124
00:05:14,070 --> 00:05:16,000
Exhale.

125
00:05:17,680 --> 00:05:19,800
Slowly inhale.

126
00:05:21,070 --> 00:05:22,920
Slowly exhale.

127
00:05:26,480 --> 00:05:28,160
He actually fell asleep.

128
00:05:29,120 --> 00:05:29,960
That little stick…

129
00:05:35,190 --> 00:05:36,190
I never expected

130
00:05:36,480 --> 00:05:37,800
such a little stick

131
00:05:37,950 --> 00:05:39,750
to work so remarkably well.

132
00:05:39,800 --> 00:05:41,240
Just a quick fix

133
00:05:41,560 --> 00:05:42,800
to relieve the pressure

134
00:05:42,800 --> 00:05:44,560
for the time being.

135
00:05:44,560 --> 00:05:45,750
Real healing

136
00:05:45,750 --> 00:05:47,480
takes time.

137
00:05:48,630 --> 00:05:49,800
Well,

138
00:05:49,950 --> 00:05:51,630
you do have some skill.

139
00:05:52,070 --> 00:05:53,120
Then from now on,

140
00:05:53,120 --> 00:05:54,270
the Prince's…

141
00:05:54,510 --> 00:05:55,680
What was it called again?

142
00:05:55,830 --> 00:05:58,390
Anxiety.

143
00:05:58,390 --> 00:06:00,070
I shall leave his care in your hands.

144
00:06:01,160 --> 00:06:03,680
I won't let you down.

145
00:06:03,950 --> 00:06:07,190
I'll ensure the Prince's well-being.

146
00:06:08,070 --> 00:06:09,430
(Fictional. Do not imitate.)
This pebble path's

147
00:06:09,430 --> 00:06:11,000
designed based

148
00:06:11,000 --> 00:06:13,430
on foot acupoints.

149
00:06:13,430 --> 00:06:16,190
Three laps beat years of medicine.

150
00:06:18,070 --> 00:06:19,240
If you don't believe me,

151
00:06:19,240 --> 00:06:21,190
just watch.

152
00:06:23,680 --> 00:06:25,310
See? Easy.

153
00:06:31,040 --> 00:06:32,750
This is for spleen meridian.

154
00:06:32,750 --> 00:06:33,800
Helps digestion.

155
00:06:33,870 --> 00:06:35,390
Walk it hard,

156
00:06:35,390 --> 00:06:37,680
you won't even feel hungry tonight.

157
00:06:39,190 --> 00:06:40,070
Easy.

158
00:06:43,390 --> 00:06:45,010
This is for kidney meridian.

159
00:06:45,010 --> 00:06:46,020
It governs vital energy.

160
00:06:46,120 --> 00:06:47,390
Your insomnia

161
00:06:47,390 --> 00:06:48,240
is caused

162
00:06:48,240 --> 00:06:49,830
by a blockage here.

163
00:06:51,630 --> 00:06:52,470
That's it.

164
00:06:54,070 --> 00:06:55,360
Easy, Your Highness.

165
00:06:56,160 --> 00:06:57,000
Don't tell me

166
00:06:57,310 --> 00:06:59,480
you're more afraid of pain than a girl?

167
00:07:01,160 --> 00:07:02,000
Shoes off.

168
00:07:04,310 --> 00:07:06,160
Your Highness, please.

169
00:07:17,680 --> 00:07:18,520
Does it hurt?

170
00:07:21,560 --> 00:07:22,400
No.

171
00:07:29,430 --> 00:07:30,510
Is it

172
00:07:30,630 --> 00:07:32,190
a pebble path?

173
00:07:32,950 --> 00:07:33,830
Your Highness.

174
00:07:34,190 --> 00:07:35,390
That's good.

175
00:07:36,000 --> 00:07:38,720
Pain means it's treatable.

176
00:07:38,950 --> 00:07:40,480
If it didn't hurt,

177
00:07:40,510 --> 00:07:41,480
you'd be in real trouble.

178
00:07:41,950 --> 00:07:43,240
Step forward.

179
00:07:44,720 --> 00:07:45,560
Stop.

180
00:07:47,630 --> 00:07:49,480
This spot is for your kidneys.

181
00:07:49,630 --> 00:07:51,310
It's exactly what you need.

182
00:07:52,070 --> 00:07:53,160
Hold on.

183
00:07:53,270 --> 00:07:55,390
One, two, three, four, five.

184
00:07:57,360 --> 00:07:58,200
How does that feel?

185
00:08:02,070 --> 00:08:02,950
I'm fine.

186
00:08:03,750 --> 00:08:05,000
One more step.

187
00:08:05,480 --> 00:08:06,320
All right.

188
00:08:06,920 --> 00:08:08,480
Make it to the end.

189
00:08:08,560 --> 00:08:09,510
No herbal bath

190
00:08:09,510 --> 00:08:11,190
for you tonight.

191
00:08:11,950 --> 00:08:12,800
Ready now.

192
00:08:13,510 --> 00:08:14,560
This time,

193
00:08:14,830 --> 00:08:16,510
he's truly met his match.

194
00:08:16,680 --> 00:08:18,160
Ready, go.

195
00:08:18,160 --> 00:08:20,510
One, two, three, four, five.

196
00:08:32,150 --> 00:08:32,990
No need.

197
00:08:35,150 --> 00:08:36,720
After this,

198
00:08:36,720 --> 00:08:39,150
your Yongquan point is half open.

199
00:08:40,080 --> 00:08:41,550
Foot soak with ginger tonight,

200
00:08:41,550 --> 00:08:42,630
then calming paste.

201
00:08:42,770 --> 00:08:43,630
Yes.

202
00:08:43,640 --> 00:08:45,480
You'll sleep well.

203
00:08:47,120 --> 00:08:48,120
And

204
00:08:48,630 --> 00:08:50,150
if I don't?

205
00:08:50,150 --> 00:08:51,910
Then we do this again tomorrow

206
00:08:51,910 --> 00:08:54,550
with sharper stones.

207
00:08:55,030 --> 00:08:55,870
No need.

208
00:08:56,960 --> 00:08:58,150
I'm sure

209
00:08:59,390 --> 00:09:00,670
I'll sleep perfectly.

210
00:09:04,840 --> 00:09:05,720
Wipe your sweat.

211
00:09:30,040 --> 00:09:30,890
Your Highness.

212
00:09:30,910 --> 00:09:31,750
Your Highness.

213
00:09:32,200 --> 00:09:33,440
Her Highness ordered you

214
00:09:33,480 --> 00:09:35,630
to follow the treatment.

215
00:09:35,630 --> 00:09:36,630
It was you

216
00:09:36,630 --> 00:09:38,630
who asked for her treatment.

217
00:09:39,240 --> 00:09:41,200
If you back out now,

218
00:09:41,550 --> 00:09:43,390
it would hardly be graceful.

219
00:09:45,500 --> 00:09:52,500
(Fictional. Do not imitate.)

220
00:10:04,720 --> 00:10:05,560
Your Highness,

221
00:10:05,750 --> 00:10:06,720
the herbal bath is ready.

222
00:10:06,720 --> 00:10:07,670
We can begin now.

223
00:10:07,750 --> 00:10:08,590
Oh.

224
00:10:11,550 --> 00:10:13,480
It's improper for us to be this close.

225
00:10:13,630 --> 00:10:14,960
Many imperial physicians

226
00:10:14,960 --> 00:10:17,000
are skilled in scraping therapy.

227
00:10:17,320 --> 00:10:18,720
There is no need

228
00:10:18,720 --> 00:10:20,000
to do it yourself.

229
00:10:20,600 --> 00:10:21,880
- Get the physician.
- Yes.

230
00:10:22,000 --> 00:10:22,840
Wait.

231
00:10:24,320 --> 00:10:26,390
This is my family's secret method.

232
00:10:26,390 --> 00:10:27,870
Not to be shared.

233
00:10:29,480 --> 00:10:30,480
Rest assured.

234
00:10:30,750 --> 00:10:32,870
To a healer, there are no genders,

235
00:10:32,870 --> 00:10:33,790
only patients.

236
00:10:34,440 --> 00:10:36,550
Buddha taught: To a pure mind,

237
00:10:36,550 --> 00:10:37,870
all is pure.

238
00:10:38,000 --> 00:10:39,360
To a clouded mind,

239
00:10:39,360 --> 00:10:41,480
all is stained.

240
00:10:42,150 --> 00:10:43,150
My mind

241
00:10:43,390 --> 00:10:44,910
is perfectly pure.

242
00:10:49,670 --> 00:10:52,360
Your Highness.

243
00:10:52,670 --> 00:10:54,080
Unless yours isn't.

244
00:10:55,390 --> 00:10:57,480
I am

245
00:10:58,150 --> 00:11:00,720
definitely aboveboard.

246
00:11:01,440 --> 00:11:03,200
Since we're both aboveboard,

247
00:11:03,200 --> 00:11:04,200
then let us begin.

248
00:11:22,390 --> 00:11:23,230
Undress me.

249
00:11:31,240 --> 00:11:33,360
Your Highness, the water is just right,

250
00:11:33,360 --> 00:11:34,550
neither cool nor too hot.

251
00:11:34,550 --> 00:11:36,320
After you soak for a quarter,

252
00:11:36,320 --> 00:11:38,360
I'll begin your scraping therapy.

253
00:12:03,120 --> 00:12:04,720
Your Highness, the time is up.

254
00:12:04,870 --> 00:12:06,120
We can begin now.

255
00:12:07,030 --> 00:12:08,600
Please bend forward.

256
00:12:19,440 --> 00:12:20,290
Your Highness.

257
00:12:20,360 --> 00:12:21,200
Let's begin.

258
00:12:28,200 --> 00:12:29,040
Your Highness.

259
00:12:29,630 --> 00:12:30,470
Are you...

260
00:12:31,150 --> 00:12:32,150
afraid of pain?

261
00:12:34,790 --> 00:12:35,630
I was

262
00:12:37,510 --> 00:12:39,200
just unprepared.

263
00:12:41,600 --> 00:12:43,120
Where itcs blocked, it hurts.

264
00:12:43,120 --> 00:12:44,440
Pain means a blockage.

265
00:12:44,790 --> 00:12:46,910
Once we clear it, you'll feel better.

266
00:12:46,910 --> 00:12:47,840
Just hang in there.

267
00:13:03,000 --> 00:13:03,840
A little longer.

268
00:13:08,550 --> 00:13:10,030
Your Highness.

269
00:13:10,030 --> 00:13:11,360
How are you feeling?

270
00:13:12,150 --> 00:13:13,200
I should've

271
00:13:13,510 --> 00:13:14,840
kept my mouth shut

272
00:13:15,670 --> 00:13:17,320
and never let her treat me.

273
00:13:21,600 --> 00:13:22,550
Why didn't you stop her?

274
00:13:22,550 --> 00:13:25,270
It's all my fault.

275
00:13:31,390 --> 00:13:32,440
Easy.

276
00:13:33,600 --> 00:13:35,670
After what Ye Jin did to me,

277
00:13:35,960 --> 00:13:36,910
my whole body aches.

278
00:13:37,440 --> 00:13:39,510
Miss Ye Jin truly didn't hold back.

279
00:13:39,750 --> 00:13:41,840
Your Highness, those marks on your back...

280
00:13:42,000 --> 00:13:43,550
Even I'm shocked.

281
00:13:43,840 --> 00:13:45,390
But strangely enough,

282
00:13:45,630 --> 00:13:46,470
Your Highness,

283
00:13:46,600 --> 00:13:47,510
your complexion

284
00:13:47,510 --> 00:13:49,600
does look much rosier.

285
00:13:50,390 --> 00:13:51,320
Rosy, my foot.

286
00:13:53,480 --> 00:13:55,440
That's bruising.

287
00:13:55,910 --> 00:13:57,240
Her tool's like

288
00:13:57,750 --> 00:13:59,240
a butcher's knife.

289
00:14:04,550 --> 00:14:08,390
Well, her methods seem to work.

290
00:14:18,850 --> 00:14:21,290
♪I am but an outsider♪

291
00:14:21,330 --> 00:14:23,490
♪Yet something drags me deeper♪

292
00:14:23,730 --> 00:14:27,770
♪Outwit the world but not the way we meet♪

293
00:14:27,770 --> 00:14:32,010
♪Splendid blooms line deadly ground♪

294
00:14:36,290 --> 00:14:39,530
♪Life's a phantom, yet I find you♪

295
00:14:39,690 --> 00:14:43,090
♪In a world of lies, you're all that's clear♪

296
00:14:43,090 --> 00:14:45,610
♪I know how this story ends♪

297
00:14:45,610 --> 00:14:50,170
♪I still want what's in your eyes♪

298
00:14:50,490 --> 00:14:54,610
♪Truth or lie—I can't tell♪

299
00:14:59,570 --> 00:15:02,890
♪You hide it all behind your lines♪

300
00:15:02,890 --> 00:15:06,170
♪So familiar, yet out of reach♪

301
00:15:06,370 --> 00:15:09,450
♪A history that no one can search♪

302
00:15:09,690 --> 00:15:12,970
♪Like you drift in from another star♪

303
00:15:13,010 --> 00:15:14,770
♪I am but an outsider♪

304
00:15:14,770 --> 00:15:17,010
♪Yet something drags me deeper♪

305
00:15:17,010 --> 00:15:21,050
♪Outwit the world but not the way we meet♪

306
00:15:21,050 --> 00:15:25,730
♪Splendid blooms line deadly ground♪

307
00:15:29,650 --> 00:15:33,050
♪Life's a phantom, yet I find you♪

308
00:15:33,050 --> 00:15:36,410
♪In a world of lies, you're all that's clear♪

309
00:15:36,410 --> 00:15:38,890
♪I know how this story ends♪

310
00:15:38,890 --> 00:15:43,050
♪I still want what's in your eyes♪

311
00:15:43,050 --> 00:15:46,330
♪When it's over and I'm gone♪

312
00:15:46,330 --> 00:15:50,130
♪Please forget me and move on♪

313
00:15:50,130 --> 00:15:56,370
♪Just let this absurd dream fade♪

314
00:15:59,530 --> 00:16:07,890
♪Snow hides our tracks♪

315
00:16:11,450 --> 00:16:21,170
♪When do I finally wake♪
